                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12780449" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2009 05:34:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like this was dropped a commit or two ago:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;r817650 &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1447&quot; title=&quot;Simple property injection &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-1447&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-1447&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should prob just be reverted to what it was - not sure we need to try and cap it and it needs the LogMergePolicy check. Though the &amp;gt;0 check makes a bit more sense to me than != -1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     if (config.mergeFactor != -1 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; getMergePolicy() instanceof LogMergePolicy) &lt;/p&gt;
{
        setMergeFactor(config.mergeFactor);
      }</comment>
                            <comment id="12780453" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2009 05:46:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So the workaround is to use the functionality of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1447&quot; title=&quot;Simple property injection &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-1447&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-1447&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;mergePolicy class=&quot;org.apache.lucene.index.LogByteSizeMergePolicy&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;int name=&quot;mergeFactor&quot;&amp;gt;3&amp;lt;/int&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/mergePolicy&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Possibly why it was taken out? But the example config was not updated to reflect, so who knows I guess.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12780592" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2009 15:21:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reminder to put this issue and workaround on solr 1.4 post release notes wiki page.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12780644" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2009 16:52:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ill wait a bit for comments and then commit. Thanks Lance!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12781447" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Mon, 23 Nov 2009 16:12:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Lance!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
